"{\"uid\": \"newsghana.com.gh-celine-dion-makes-triumphant-return-at-paris-olympics-opening-ceremony\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Canadian music icon Celine Dion made a stunning comeback to the stage at the Paris Summer Olympics opening ceremony on Friday.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 126, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 14, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Music_of_Canada\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Canadian music\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Music_of_Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Music_of_Canada\"}, {\"begin\": 20, \"end\": 31, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Celine_Dion\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.714421729864843e-44, \"text\": \"Celine Dion\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Celine_Dion\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Celine_Dion\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The superstar performer closed the ceremony with a breathtaking rendition of Edith Piaf's \\\"L'Hymne \\u00e0 l'amour\\\" from the first stage of the Eiffel Tower, showcasing her vocal prowess in a beaded white gown.\", \"from\": 130, \"to\": 334, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 207, \"end\": 217, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u00c9dith_Piaf\", \"score\": 0.9999999912249677, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Edith Piaf\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u00c9dith_Piaf\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u00c9dith_Piaf\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dion's performance, which followed the lighting of the Olympic cauldron, was met with high praise.\", \"from\": 338, \"to\": 436, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"NBC commentator Kelly Clarkson described Dion as \\\"a vocal athlete,\\\"reflecting the moment's awe.\", \"from\": 437, \"to\": 532, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 437, \"end\": 440, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.9940255106015365, \"rank\": 0.005998277639427014, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}, {\"begin\": 453, \"end\": 467, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Clarkson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kelly Clarkson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Clarkson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Clarkson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am honored to have performed tonight, for the Paris 2024 Opening Ceremony, and so full of joy to be back in one of my very favorite cities!\", \"from\": 534, \"to\": 675, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Most of all, I am so happy to be celebrating these amazing athletes, with all their stories of sacrifice and determination, pain and\\u2026pic.twitter.com/Ak6iKfhgzX  - Celine Dion (@celinedion)July 27, 2024    This performance marks Dion's first live concert since her diagnosis of stiff person syndrome-a rare, progressive condition affecting the nervous system.\", \"from\": 676, \"to\": 1034, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Dion announced in December 2022 that she was stepping away from professional commitments to focus on her health, citing difficulties with singing due to the condition.\", \"from\": 1035, \"to\": 1202, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Before this, Dion's last live performance was in March 2020 in New Jersey.\", \"from\": 1206, \"to\": 1280, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1269, \"end\": 1279, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Jersey\", \"score\": 0.9956182446262213, \"rank\": 0.004245863065445915, \"text\": \"New Jersey\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Jersey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Jersey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite her diagnosis, Dion remains determined to continue performing, as she revealed in her recent documentary, \\\"I Am: Celine Dion,\\\"which premiered on Amazon.\", \"from\": 1281, \"to\": 1441, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1434, \"end\": 1440, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Music\", \"score\": 0.9094116358928697, \"rank\": 0.07731414672688702, \"text\": \"Amazon\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Music\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Music\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The documentary details the challenges of living with the syndrome, including painful muscle spasms and rigidity.\", \"from\": 1442, \"to\": 1555, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Let the games begin!Sending love and luck to all competitors.- Celine xx\\u2026#paris2024#openingceremonypic.twitter.com/84aJP9AGjw  - Celine Dion (@celinedion)July 26, 2024    Dion's resilience was evident earlier this year when she appeared at the Grammy Awards to present the final trophy.\", \"from\": 1557, \"to\": 1843, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Her return to the stage in Paris underscores her unwavering commitment to her music career.\", \"from\": 1844, \"to\": 1935, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1871, \"end\": 1876, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.418668286772173e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The opening ceremony also featured Lady Gaga, who launched the event with a \\\"Mon truc en plume\\\"performance by Zizi Jeanmaire along the Seine River.\", \"from\": 1939, \"to\": 2086, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1974, \"end\": 1983, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lady Gaga\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\"}, {\"begin\": 2049, \"end\": 2063, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.or